{"tid":1197254,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"組成一條有力嘅人鏈","createTime":"2019-06-10T02:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T06:43:18.000Z","uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3776d1a16c004a5a7f2b39f72046a24180b1045a","tid":1197254,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T02:43:36.000Z","msg":"左手q右手其實唔係有力嘅人鏈 而且中門大開 容易受傷<br />\n<br />\n更有效人鏈如下<br />\n<br />\n(最左)A B C D E (最右)<br />\nX X X X X<br />\n<br />\n以上為10個人 A-E為前排 X為後排支援<br />\n<br />\nStep1: 前排每人嘅左手成曲尺姿勢護於胸前（💪手臂要喺心口前面）<br />\n<br />\nStep2: A嘅右手繞過B嘅背脊 捉實C嘅褲頭（最好捉皮帶） B右手繞過C捉住D嘅褲頭/皮帶 如此類推 直到E(最右)<br />\nE右手冇野捉 咁就轉右手護前 左手捉住C嘅褲頭/皮帶<br />\n<br />\nStep3: 後方X雙手支撐前排<br />\n<br />\n以上係基本構造<br />\n<br />\n有效人鏈仲要有裝備<br />\n前排多出嘅一隻手可以拎盾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外請多著保護裝備 護膝護腕護肘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n排陣：<br />\n如果多人 多到爆6條線 可以咁<br />\nA⋯B⋯C⋯D⋯E<br />\nXXXXXXXXXXX<br />\nXXXXXXXXXXX <br />\n<br />\n支援唔好多過三排 保持機動性<br />\n<br />\n如果小規模 唔多夠人 可以用金字塔式<br />\nA⋯B⋯C⋯D⋯E<br />\n⋯X .    X .   X .    X<br />\n  ⋯   X.   X.   X <br />\n<br />\n需要步伐一致 保持推進 同時發力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173589db5d5bf7b5c9a4e1e003b84baf246ad5a5","tid":1197254,"uid":18605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T02:46:51.000Z","msg":"以往比警察一推就散 係因為啲人各有各推 容易分散"},{"pid":"ada79c0b2d1eef2848f0cace85b3a6deb23fe696","tid":1197254,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}